etomica.paracetamol

Class CoordinateDefinitionParacetamol

  • java.lang.Object
    • etomica.normalmode.CoordinateDefinition
      • etomica.normalmode.CoordinateDefinitionMolecule
        • etomica.paracetamol.CoordinateDefinitionParacetamol
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class CoordinateDefinitionParacetamol
extends CoordinateDefinitionMolecule
implements java.io.Serializable
    CoordinateDefinition implementation for paracetamol molecule. The class takes the first space.D values of u to be real space displacements of the molecule center of mass from its nominal position and 3 rotational displacements.
